    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『皐月賞』を目前に控えたある日。彼女は\r\nトレーナーに、走ることが楽しくなくなって\nしまったと、伝えるのだった。",
            "enText": "One day, just before the Satsuki-sho, she\ntold her trainer that she no longer\nenjoyed running. She told her trainer that\nshe was no longer enjoying running.",
