        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "トレーナーは気落ちするマルゼンスキーへ、\r\n彼女に憧れてトレーニングに励む後輩たちの\n姿を見せる。",
            "enText": "The trainer shows a depressed Maruzensky\nthe younger members of the team who admire\nher and want to train with her.",
